Inside, the aroma of coffee and catered snacks fills the air while event staff scan registrations, log attendance metrics, and distribute branded tote bags containing notebooks, pens, water bottles, and phone chargers. Career counselors assist students, emphasizing the importance of maintaining eye contact during introductions and guiding them toward applicable industries. Concurrent workshops on networking etiquette and an alumni panel discussing preparation for technical interviews occur in adjoining classrooms, alongside a resume review table sponsored by the engineering society. As the final hour approaches, announcement chimes signal the end of the fair, with excitement buzzing as interview sign-up sheets begin to fill.

Inside, recruiters distribute branded tote bags filled with notebooks, pens, water bottles, and phone chargers, while the aroma of coffee and catered snacks fills the air. Career center staff log attendance metrics and scan registrations on laptops, handing out lanyards. Career counselors emphasize the importance of maintaining eye contact during introductions and guide students toward applicable industries. Attendees utilize kiosks and tablets to upload resumes to the fair database. Concurrent workshops on networking etiquette and a panel discussing technical interview preparation occur in an adjoining classroom, alongside a resume review table sponsored by the engineering society. As the final hour approaches, announcement chimes signal the end of the fair, and interview sign-up sheets begin to fill with names.
